    Scope and Contents
Mason County Illinois  Family.

Marriage certificates for James W. Shelton and Sarah C. Smith (1884) and Sarah Shelton &amp; John  Armstrong (1898); birth dates for Sarah Shelton  &amp; John Armstrong and  their children (Clara Belle, Albert, Lula May); and an unsigned temperance pledge.  Except for the 1884 marriage,  all papers appear to have come from a family bible.  
  
